{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-010__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·010.1", "text_original": "驕人好好，勞人草草。蒼天蒼天！視彼驕人，矜此勞人！", "text_normalized": "驕人好好，勞人草草。蒼天蒼天！視彼驕人，矜此勞人！", "notes": "巷伯 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-jienanshan-010__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-jienanshan-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·節南山之什·010.2", "text_original": "彼譖人者，誰適與謀？取彼譖人，投畀豺虎。\n豺虎不食，投畀有北。有北不受，投畀有昊。", "text_normalized": "彼譖人者，誰適與謀？取彼譖人，投畀豺虎。\n豺虎不食，投畀有北。有北不受，投畀有昊。", "notes": "巷伯 Chinese stanza 2."}
